Crée ta musique et des beats

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 本格的なトラックメイキングに
A sound studio in your pocket

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A refreshingly simple take on music-making, Auxy lets you create beats simply by placing colorful squares on grids. With the intuitive modular interface, it’s easy to arrange blocks, tinker with their composition, and create complicated beats. Once you’ve found the sound you’re looking for, you can adjust the tempo, key, and effects on the fly—then record it and export to MIDI.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: A refreshingly simple take on music-making using modular blocks.
